{{地區用詞|tw=鎖定螢幕|cn=锁定屏幕'''、'''锁屏|sg=cn|my=cn|hk=鎖定熒幕|mo=hk|start={{lang-en|Lock screen}}|as=稱作|before='''|after='''}}，或稱'''鎖定畫面'''，是一款在各個[[操作系统|作業系統]]都有得到應用的[[用户界面|用户界面]]。它們透過要求用戶進行特定操作，來實現[[存取控制|存取控制]]。用戶可能需要在锁定螢幕上輸入密碼、特定的組合按鍵，或使用裝置的[[觸控式螢幕|觸控式螢幕]]來進行[[手势识别|手势识别]]，才能解鎖裝置，存取特定內容。

锁定螢幕的介面設計各有不同。有些锁定螢幕只是一个簡單的[[登入|登录屏幕]]。不過也有些锁定螢幕會顯示目前時間、日期、天氣、[[推送技术|推送]]、後台媒體控制界面、應用程式捷徑（比如開啟相機的捷徑）、用戶自行輸入的資訊<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cnet.com/how-to/first-responders-can-help-you-even-when-your-phone-is-locked/|title=First responders can help you even when your phone is locked|last=Cipriani|first=Jason|website=CNET|language=en|access-date=2020-01-03|archive-date=2021-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210218065543/https://www.cnet.com/how-to/first-responders-can-help-you-even-when-your-phone-is-locked/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.phonearena.com/news/How-to-add-owner-info-on-your-Android-lock-screen-helpful-in-case-you-lose-your-device_id66968|title=How to add owner info on your Android lock screen (helpful in case you lose your device)|last=T|first=Florin|website=Phone Arena|language=en-US|access-date=2020-01-03|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227223511/https://www.phonearena.com/news/How-to-add-owner-info-on-your-Android-lock-screen-helpful-in-case-you-lose-your-device_id66968|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.androidcentral.com/lock-screen-customization-dead|title=Lock screen customization is dead|date=2018-06-18|website=Android Central|language=en|access-date=2020-01-03|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111213527/https://www.androidcentral.com/lock-screen-customization-dead|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==各個平台的锁定螢幕==

===行動作業系統===
[[File:Android_4.3_on_LG_Nexus_4.png|thumb]]圖標來解鎖。]]
[[智能手机|智能手机]]及[[平板電腦|平板電腦]]一般都是採用建基於手勢的锁定螢幕。由{{link-en|Neonode|Neonode}}生產的手機需透過向右滑動觸控式螢幕來解鎖。[[蘋果公司|蘋果公司]]的[[iPhone|iPhone]]及[[iPad|iPad]]在[[iOS_10|iOS 10]]之前，也是採用類近機制來解鎖——把螢幕向右滑動。自iOS 5开始，向另一個方向滑動則會開啟「相機」。到了iOS 7，設計者為了配合全新的視覺設計風格，而決定移除滑塊；用戶仍可透過滑動螢幕來解鎖。鎖定畫面上亦會顯示日期、時間、最新通知、音频控制介面<ref name=pcw-ios5>{{cite web|title=The 5 best features in Apple's iOS 5|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/229866/The_5_best_features_in_Apple_iOS_5.html|publisher=PC World|accessdate=2013-02-13|archive-date=2016-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160810061456/http://www.pcworld.com/article/229866/The_5_best_features_in_Apple_iOS_5.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=macworld-ios7design>{{cite web|title=Get to know iOS 7: Design changes|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/2048733/get-to-know-ios-7-design-changes.html|work=MacWorld|accessdate=2013-12-04|archive-date=2017-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170619020111/http://www.macworld.com/article/2048733/get-to-know-ios-7-design-changes.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。iOS 10的鎖定畫面改動了不少，其不用手勢識別去作解鎖觸發機制 ，改以Home鍵來解鎖。用戶仍可以滑動螢幕的方式來開啟「相機」。向右滑則會開啟左邊的小工具頁面<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.techradar.com/how-to/how-to-use-the-lock-screen-in-ios-10|title=How to use the Lock screen in iOS 10|work=TechRadar|access-date=2017-11-13|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714100550/https://www.techradar.com/how-to/how-to-use-the-lock-screen-in-ios-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.cnet.com/how-to/heres-how-to-navigate-the-ios-10-lock-screen/|title=How to use the iPhone's new, confusing lock screen|work=CNET|access-date=2017-11-13|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025045517/https://www.cnet.com/how-to/heres-how-to-navigate-the-ios-10-lock-screen/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由於[[iPhone_X|iPhone X]]及[[iPad_Pro|iPad Pro]]取消了實體Home鍵，故用戶需透過從屏幕底部向上滑動來解鎖<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.wired.com/2017/11/review-iphone-x/|title=iPhone X Review: All Up In Your Face ID|last=Pierce|first=David|work=Wired|access-date=2017-11-13|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117164646/https://www.wired.com/2017/11/review-iphone-x/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pcmag.com/feature/365215/how-to-navigate-the-ipad-pro-without-a-home-button|title=How to Navigate the iPad Pro (Without a Home Button)|last=Whitney|first=Lance|website=PCMAG|language=en|access-date=2020-01-04|archive-date=2020-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200104013906/https://www.pcmag.com/feature/365215/how-to-navigate-the-ipad-pro-without-a-home-button|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

起初[[Android|Android]]並沒有採用建基於手勢的锁定螢幕，使用者需按下手机的菜单键來解鎖。到了Android 2.0，才有了锁定螢幕。它左右兩邊各有一個圖標：一个用於解鎖，另一个則用於设置音量。把圖標拖至曲线条中間位置即可使用相關功能。在Android 2.1，開發者移除了曲线条，改用兩條放在左右兩端的直條去進行上述操作<ref name=verge-androidvisual>{{cite web|title=Android: A visual history|url=https://www.theverge.com/2011/12/7/2585779/android-history|publisher=The Verge|accessdate=2013-02-14|archive-date=2013-01-21|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DpDvrrwH?url=http://www.theverge.com/2011/12/7/2585779/android-history|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Android 3.0則採用了全新的設計：要把圓形[[挂锁|挂锁]]圖標拖至一個大圓形外才可解鎖<ref name=ars-xoom-lock>{{cite web|title=Ars reviews the Motorola Xoom|url=https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2011/03/ars-reviews-the-motorola-xoom/3/|publisher=Ars Technica|accessdate=2013-02-13|archive-date=2017-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170915113643/https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2011/03/ars-reviews-the-motorola-xoom/3/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在Android 4.0，用戶可以滑動螢幕的方式來開啟「相機」。在Android 4.1則可以透過向上滑動進入Google搜尋頁面<ref name=sg-4.0demo>{{cite web|title=Android 4.0 ICS demo: Active voice dictation, Unlock to camera, and more|url=http://www.slashgear.com/android-4-0-ics-demo-active-voice-dictation-unlock-to-camera-and-more-17196349/|publisher=SlashGear|accessdate=2013-02-14|archive-date=2017-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170915161156/https://www.slashgear.com/android-4-0-ics-demo-active-voice-dictation-unlock-to-camera-and-more-17196349/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=tr-androidjellybean>{{cite web|title=Android 4.1 and Android 4.2 combine to make the ultimate Jelly Bean|url=http://www.techradar.com/reviews/pc-mac/software/operating-systems/android-jelly-bean-1087230/review/1#articleContent|publisher=TechRadar|accessdate=2013-02-14|archive-date=2017-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170324003926/http://www.techradar.com/reviews/pc-mac/software/operating-systems/android-jelly-bean-1087230/review/1#articleContent|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Android 4.2的锁定螢幕出現了更進一步的轉變，使得用戶可以透過從左下角往右滑動，開啟小工具頁面。從右下角往左滑動則能開啓「相機」<ref name=tr-androidjellybean/>。Android的鎖定類型有密碼鎖定、PIN碼鎖定、圖形鎖定、[[指紋識別|指紋鎖定]]、[[臉部辨識系統|人臉鎖定]]<ref name=verge-androidvisual/>。

其他厂商的Android手機通常採用與原生Android不同的锁定螢幕設計：[[HTC_Sense|HTC Sense]]的部分版本透過拖動下方的金属环來解鎖，部分應用程式亦可透過拖動圖標至金属环的方式開啟<ref name=gsma-desirex>{{cite web|title=HTC Desire X review: Needs and wants|url=http://www.gsmarena.com/htc_desire_x-review-847p4.php|publisher=GSM Arena|accessdate=2013-02-14|archive-date=2017-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170417062244/http://www.gsmarena.com/htc_desire_x-review-847p4.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[三星電子|三星]]設備則只要在锁定螢幕上任意滑動即可解鎖（装有[[TouchWiz|TouchWiz Nature]]的設備則會額外加入涟漪或炫光效果）。三星的锁定螢幕跟HTC有共通之處，上面同樣可以加入應用程式捷徑<ref name=ndtv-s3jb42>{{cite web|title=Samsung Galaxy S III Android 4.2.2 firmware leaked, reveals some Galaxy S4 software features|url=http://gadgets.ndtv.com/mobiles/news/samsung-galaxy-s-iii-android-422-firmware-leaked-reveals-some-galaxy-s4-software-features-369596|work=NDTV|accessdate=2013-06-18|archive-date=2017-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170701135451/http://gadgets.ndtv.com/mobiles/news/samsung-galaxy-s-iii-android-422-firmware-leaked-reveals-some-galaxy-s4-software-features-369596|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=gsma-siiimini>{{cite web|title=Samsung I8190 Galaxy S III mini review: The Halfling|url=http://www.gsmarena.com/samsung_galaxy_s_iii_mini-review-857p4.php|publisher=GSM Arena|accessdate=2013-02-14|archive-date=2020-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114113340/https://www.gsmarena.com/samsung_galaxy_s_iii_mini-review-857p4.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

一些[[廣告軟體|廣告軟體]]會劫持預設锁定螢幕，在上面顯示[[网络广告|廣告]]。2017年11月，[[Google_Play|Play 商店]]正式禁止非锁定螢幕應用程式在锁定螢幕上顯示廣告<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2017/12/google-bans-android-developers-from-adding-lock-screen-ads/|title=Google bans Android developers from adding lock screen ads|work=Ars Technica|access-date=2017-12-01|language=en-us|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118001101/https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2017/12/google-bans-android-developers-from-adding-lock-screen-ads/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===桌上作業系統===
在[[Windows_NT|Windows NT]]，用戶已可透過操作「鎖定」一台電腦。在鎖定後會顯示登入畫面，用戶需輸入正確密碼才能解鎖。從[[Windows_XP|Windows XP]]開始，用戶可以改以[[快捷键|快捷键]]{{keypress|Win|L}}進行鎖定操作<ref name=ms-xplock>{{cite web|title=How to Quickly Lock Your Computer and Use Other Windows Logo Shortcut Keys|url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/294317|publisher=Microsoft|accessdate=2013-02-13|archive-date=2015-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150228210219/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/294317|dead-url=no}}</ref>。為了使[[Windows_8|Windows 8]]更為貼近行動作業系統，開發者重新設計了它的鎖定畫面，並容許用户自行選擇鎖定畫面的[[桌布_(使用者介面)|背景]]。此外鎖定畫面还会显示时钟、行事曆、來自應用程式的通知。用戶需透過向上拖動鼠標或觸摸屏來解鎖裝置<ref name=supersite-win8lock>{{cite web|title=Windows 8 Feature Focus: Lock Screen|url=http://winsupersite.com/article/windows8/windows-8-feature-focus-lock-screen-144656|publisher=SuperSite for Windows|accessdate=2013-02-14|archive-date=2017-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312124405/http://winsupersite.com/article/windows8/windows-8-feature-focus-lock-screen-144656|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[Windows_10|Windows 10]]的鎖定畫面設計與Windows 8類同。用戶還可以在其鎖定畫面上使用[[Cortana|Cortana]]智能個人助理。它的背景圖片則可以幻燈片秀的方式定時轉換，或由{{link-en|Windows焦點|Windows Spotlight}}提供<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.pcmag.com/article/348390/how-to-use-and-tweak-your-windows-10-lock-screen|title=How to Use and Tweak Your Windows 10 Lock Screen|work=PCMAG|access-date=2018-11-13|language=en|archive-date=2019-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191111143403/https://www.pcmag.com/article/348390/how-to-use-and-tweak-your-windows-10-lock-screen|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theverge.com/2015/4/29/8514345/windows-spotlight-lock-screen-with-ads|title=Microsoft wants to put ads on the Windows 10 lock screen|work=The Verge|access-date=2018-11-13|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130163819/https://www.theverge.com/2015/4/29/8514345/windows-spotlight-lock-screen-with-ads|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

部分[[类Unix系统|类Unix系统]]的鎖定畫面建基於像XScreenSaver和gnome-screensaver般的[[螢幕保護裝置|螢幕保護裝置]]<ref name=xs-faq>{{cite web|last=Zawinski|first=Jamie|title=XScreenSaver FAQ|url=http://www.jwz.org/xscreensaver/faq.html|accessdate=2013-02-13|archive-date=2021-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420124819/https://www.jwz.org/xscreensaver/faq.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=h-gnomelock>{{cite web|title=GNOME screen lock ineffective in openSUSE Linux - Update|url=http://www.h-online.com/open/news/item/GNOME-screen-lock-ineffective-in-openSUSE-Linux-Update-928794.html|publisher=The H|accessdate=2013-02-13|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121115604/http://www.h-online.com/open/news/item/GNOME-screen-lock-ineffective-in-openSUSE-Linux-Update-928794.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

